product.name: CoverGirl Liquiline Blast Eyeliner
product.description:
With liquiline blast, you'll get all the intensity and staying power of a
 liquid with ease and blendability of a pencil. Use the 
liner as-is for intense definition or smoke-it-out with the built-in 
smudger end for a subtle, smoky look.Features: Liquid-like formula + the ease of a pencil applicatorSmudger tip lets you customize your intensity
